This is to inform you that on June 4, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
S.B. NO. 3069, S.D. 1, H.D. 1, RELATING TO CIVIL SERVICE EXEMPT
C.D. 1 POSITIONS WITHIN THE DEPARTMENT OF
ACCOUNTING AND GENERAL SERVICES.
